@page "/"

<PageTitle>Learn Cosmos DB</PageTitle>

<div class="hero">
    <h1>Learn Azure Cosmos DB</h1>
    <p>An interactive learning platform for exploring Azure Cosmos DB concepts.</p>
</div>

<h2>Learning Modules</h2>
<div class="module-grid">
    <a href="modules/datamodeling" class="module-card">
        <div class="module-title">Data Modeling</div>
        <div class="module-desc">Demonstrates how document modeling affects query cost (RU), performance, and user experience using a movie database. Compare four models: Single, Embedded, Reference, and Hybrid.</div>
    </a>
    <a href="modules/indexing" class="module-card">
        <div class="module-title">Indexing</div>
        <div class="module-desc">See how indexing strategies affect write cost (RU). Simulate user browsing events written to three containers with different indexing policies: Default, Implicit, and Explicit.</div>
    </a>
</div>

